{
  "stem": "1316.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We didn't hear from them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Even the leaders, as we know later, the leaders of the bund ran away, ran to Russia, where they were arrested.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I think this is an important point in general for the Holocaust, that the leadership didn't prepare the masses.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't tell them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't realize, or they didn't make them realize the danger, the mortal danger that the Germans are for the Jews.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jews remembered the Germans from the First World War.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so they-- and they didn't-- many people run.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they didn't-- there was no mass evacuation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was their only chance-- the only chance to save Polish Jewry, to mass evacuate because-- to the Russian side because at the first weeks, where the border was open, my wife and her sister-- two sisters-- came over the border, even a few months later by the end of the year.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So those-- a few hundred thousand left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were saved.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "More-- most of them were survived that when the border was cut down, was closed down.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the fate of Polish Jewry was--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--was--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, on the seventh-- on the seventh day-- it was a Friday-- I went over to my-- she was my girlfriend.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used to go out already the-- for a year.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For the last year, we went out seriously, went around.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was in the same organization.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I went over to her house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I saw two men.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "One was her brother-in-law.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "His name was [POLISH], a tall man, a nice young man.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He just die a year ago.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He married my wife's sister.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Her name was [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They married.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was a carpenter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was from the Ukraine, but he worked-- he settled in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He worked there.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
